item.title: SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Software_Component_Virtual_OperatingSystem_Microsoft
item.description: SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Software_Component_Virtual_OperatingSystem_Microsoft Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Software_Component_Virtual_OperatingSystem_Microsoft data type contains general information relating to a single SoftLayer billing item for a Microsoft operating system software components on virtual machines. Local allowCancellationFlag Flag to check if a billing item can be cancelled. 1 = yes. 0 = no. Type: integer associatedBillingItemId This is sometimes populated for orphan billing items that are not attached to servers.
